  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Achieving local solutions to displacement crises in Somalia: a human security approach to durable solutions</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project takes a human security approach to enable and empower communities and local leadership to identify the localized, multidimensional and multi-sectoral factors impacting their security; the drivers of conflict and displacement; and the capacities and strengths of the community. They will also be capacitated to discuss, plan, implement and monitor activities aimed at addressing all dimensions of human insecurity.</narrative>
  </description>
